# `po/*.po.in` and translations

- After changing strings extracted via xgettext (including `navit_shipped.xml` via generated `navit_shipped.c`), run **`make locales`** from a CMake build under `po/`, then sync generated `*.po` into **`po/*.po.in`** so CI `check_po` passes.
- **`msgmerge` fails** on duplicate `msgid` in the same file—each `msgid` must appear once per `.po.in`.
- When copying build outputs to `po/*.po.in`, exclude transient files such as `navit_tmp.po`.
